{"tid":2024394,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱愛共產主義既人入黎，我哋一齊建立一個共產香港","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T19:21:36.000Z","uid":356238,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07f2105de991cfe015692fae721200400b9b7b9d","tid":2024394,"uid":356238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"真心buy 馬克思主義！<br />\n<br />\n打倒地主，原居民都算係貴族既一派<br />\n到時要佢哋班士佬地產佬跪玻璃，重新分地，人人可以即刻上樓<br />\n<br />\n做咩工等政府派，做又36唔做又36，人人都係政府工<br />\n<br />\n食又唔駛煩，到時整翻人民公社，反正有大獲飯食<br />\n<br />\n希望香港可以盡快似中國大陸五十年代一樣<br />\n<br />\n三面紅旗！大躍進！全面大煉鋼！<br />\n<br />\n香港人全民共產！共產主義萬歲！"},{"pid":"96a82566e8bb790d5a83e2bf1e0b1460b832a2ba","tid":2024394,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a><br />\n<br />\n我地抗爭要成功 首要改變返我地套mindset<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024244</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8ce91bb561fb8c74915b45579a2abcaaa91503b","tid":2024394,"uid":211941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"支持成立香港共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e85ead5817ad9cf05ffd0b258061c7f97946826","tid":2024394,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"高官全部被共產先"},{"pid":"606ae2ec9ddfb34d41aab30436a683ebf43b8d7e","tid":2024394,"uid":356238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e85ead5817ad9cf05ffd0b258061c7f97946826","tid":2024394,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"高官全部被共產先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"全部均等分配！"},{"pid":"9b53b772e32217eb51337daa3c7188779712b8ea","tid":2024394,"uid":3311